      "role": "user",
      "content": "hey, i'm working on a campaign for a new ultra-premium watch line. it's like, really high-end stuff, hundreds of thousands of dollars. can u help me build out a detailed customer persona for the ideal buyer? i need to know their age, background, lifestyle, etc to help our creative team.",
